    "description": {
      "zh": "7.92x57毫米软尖弹（SP）是一款196格令的软尖头子弹，由Rifle Line弹药公司生产，适用于狩猎、家庭防卫及靶场练习。尽管该弹头主要针对有生目标设计，但击穿大多数软质护甲仍旧绰绰有余。",
      "en": "7.92x57mm Soft Point (SP) is a 196 grain round with a soft-point bullet; intended for hunting, home defense, and target practice, produced by Rifle Line Ammunition. This round, despite it's aim towards flesh-based target, is still plenty capable at penetrating most soft armors."
